{"type": "article", "id": 48719, "title": "摩拜推出了撸猫 AR 单车，微信上线小游戏 | 乙方日报", "description": "这里有营销和营销人相关的一切", "date": "2017-12-29T04:40:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29, "name": "Top 15"}, {"id": 1928, "name": "AR"}, {"id": 33748, "name": "摩拜"}, {"id": 1494, "name": "网易"}], "category": 18, "column": 31, "author": 26306, "comment_count": 15, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20171229121256zPmuLsipyehrgJ4M.gif", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">又是跨界</h3><p><strong></strong><a href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzAxMzYxNjE1Ng==&amp;mid=2651552512&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=1af0d3f08cddfa3b1951d52f80b59b0e&amp;chksm=80600e73b7178765997849043247a8ba6b2d1ecb5e1b1c513b201de6b8308c89e727842ac1a8&amp;mpshare=1&amp;scene=1&amp;srcid=1229EbAhLlFglmNy8siUYPht&amp;key=1c2aaa2ef4c83e3a0fe51ddcd3519326329fc0295723a303a3982debad26242bce21730e657bd80485a188ab2f38e8ed4c5061935f60358825dfa839e89392cd746eb0778b675436ea7a4ac3145f9292&amp;ascene=0&amp;uin=MTIyNTYzODY0MA%3D%3D&amp;devicetype=iMac+MacBookAir6%2C2+OSX+OSX+10.10.5+build(14F2511)&amp;version=11000006&amp;lang=zh_CN&amp;pass_ticket=9UXChJmLw2AEWbkd%2BVoZOsTPbjVoXLLrPhEQnEPmNxzN%2F8oRA2Pd1sVuEXiYRNth\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>猫王收音机和喜茶</strong><strong>推出限量版跨界新年礼盒</strong></a><strong>，</strong>礼盒只送不卖，礼盒内含猫王开运收音机和&nbsp;2018 年全年的喜茶特权，<a href=\"http://lingfei.f1-soft.com/sortition/index.php?1514520284\" rel=\"nofollow\">点击这里查看 H5 活动</a>。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229120615p2jBEbTdU5hFYA9m.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667671\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p><a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/43055\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>网易 AR 的平台型产品网易洞见和摩拜单车做了个“撸猫营销”</b></a>，用户只需使用网易洞见 APP 扫描投放于摩拜单车上的 AR 识别物，就可以在单车的车筐上扫出日思夜想的萌猫。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229120815mKibEkHLS2ZrNqXo.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.704881\" data-format=\"png\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\"></p><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229120946vbxq1cUO5tQFGB70.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.556250\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><p></p><h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">值得一提的案例</h3><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24844.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>方太水槽洗碗机的广告《妈妈的时间机器》出了第二支广告“鼓手篇”</b></a>。该系列广告突破了以往妈妈为主角广告的那种刻板印象，所谓“时间机器”，是指妈妈们也有自己的人生梦想，而洗碗机可以帮她们省出时间去做更多自己想做的事情。广告挺燃，阿姨练鼓那段让人想到《爆裂鼓手》。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=v0518c3spxy&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/projects/24840.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>奥美给肯德基做了个年末的“扎心了老铁”桶</b></a>。在今年肯德基出了那么多神经兮兮的广告之后，突然走心并不是很习惯。</p><div class=\"com-insert-embed com-insert-embeds\">\r\n\t<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n\t\t<iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"https://v.qq.com/iframe/player.html?vid=h0525mno3yr&amp;tiny=0&amp;auto=0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></iframe>\r\n\t</figure>\r\n\t\r\n</div><h3>最后，也挺重要</h3><p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.thedrum.com/news/2017/12/27/amazon-set-introduce-its-advertising-products-combat-facebook-and-google-2018\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>亚马逊计划在网站和产品外出售广告</b></a>。亚马逊也在与第三方移动公司合作（如 Kargo），让广告出现在电视和移动设备的屏幕上。其他平台的实验包括电子商务搜索和视频产品平台的测试。<br></p><p><a href=\"https://www.digitaling.com/articles/42490.html\" rel=\"nofollow\"><b>微信版本 6.6.1 安卓、iOS 同时更新</b></a>，新增小游戏功能，允许开发游戏；取消小程序置顶，增加小程序任务栏；小程序支持快捷切换；游戏板块新增小游戏专题，有隐私设置。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20171229121026V3wGEMKXZcxpoYPH.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.859375\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><p class=\"\">题图来源：<a href=\"http://creative.adquan.com/show/43055\" rel=\"nofollow\">adquan</a></p>"}